C# & .NET Projects Portfolio

This repository contains several C# projects I developed during my training with the .NET Framework. These projects showcase my growing expertise in back-end programming, data management, and full-stack web development using ASP.NET MVC.

Projects Overview

üöó Car Insurance Quote App  
An ASP.NET MVC web application that calculates personalized car insurance quotes based on user input and a set of business rules. The app collects driver and vehicle details to generate accurate insurance pricing.

*Key Features:*  
- Dynamic quote calculation logic considering driver age, vehicle details, driving history, and coverage type  
- Admin dashboard for staff to view and manage all issued insurance quotes  
- Form input validation to ensure data integrity and user-friendly error feedback  
- Persistent data storage using SQL Server and Entity Framework for reliable data management  

*Technologies Used:*  
ASP.NET MVC, C#, Entity Framework, SQL Server

---

üèà NFL Statistics Viewer  
A web-based application designed to track and display NFL player and team statistics, tailored for fantasy football players and sports enthusiasts.

*Key Features:*
- Database-driven storage and retrieval of detailed player and team stats  
- Use of the Code First approach with Entity Framework to create and manage the database schema  
- Responsive and interactive user interface enabling easy data exploration and visualization  

*Technologies Used:*  
ASP.NET MVC, Entity Framework, C#, LINQ

